Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:48.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A whole colony of Demon Bats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:05.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're the Demon Bats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:13.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're heading for the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:14.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:16.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:18.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you gawking at!\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:49.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The village...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:51.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't grieve over them, Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're the ones who\nharassed you and your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:59.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you protect me with\nthe barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:02.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will spare your mother's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Annihilate the entire village!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-reaver, Soul-stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:21.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You old bastard!\NYou won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're an eyesore, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Attaway, Miroku!\NLet 'em have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're late!\NWhere were you dawdling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How many of 'em are\nthere anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get the small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:10.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It turned back the Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:21.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as Shiori is around,\NI cannot use my Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:25.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NCan't make a move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:27.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there some way to separate\NShiori from Taigokumaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If there is, please do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:34.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please! Do something about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll all be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The villagers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:45.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I don't need to be asked\nto kill Taigokumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:48.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But that's only after\NI get Shiori back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, Shiori is on\ntheir side!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want me to kill\nher, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori is a demon's child,\nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori was given up by her mother\nto the Demon Bats
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to save your village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:17.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, doesn't Inuyasha\ndespise people like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:21.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, he's been through\nthe same experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you hear, Shiori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:30.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:33.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you return to a\nvillage like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,no good may come of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:39.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you still want to return?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:43.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He came earlier to the nest today\nwith Mommy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:47.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you still want to return home,\NI will help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:48.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:50.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:55.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You think you can defeat\nme, Taigokumaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:10.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Brat, you're also a half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You reek with the smell\nof a half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're thinking of your\nown situation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:22.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and feeling sorry for Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Not likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate old rotten bats\nlike you, is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:33.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Half-demon?\NHe's the same as me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori! Make up your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:39.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to stay\nor return home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to go home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To Mommy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mommy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you, Shiori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unless you continue to protect\nme by guarding the barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:03.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,your mother will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:13.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brat! Don't confuse Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:14.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:16.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just protect yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that the power of the barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good work, Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's what you must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:49.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If just a part of Taigokumaru's body\ngoes outside the barrier,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I'd have a chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:56.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But doesn't Shiori have the power to\nadjust the size of the barrier?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out, everyone! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The village...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no use for\nthis village any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get rid of all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Taigokumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:42.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Missus...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:47.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This village was peaceful\nwhen your son, Tsukuyomaru, was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because Tsukuyomaru\nprotected us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:54.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wished a happy life for\NShiori and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so he prevented attacks\non our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:04.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please honor Tsukuyomaru's wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Honor his wish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:26.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsukuyomaru was my son,\nbut he was a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:32.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Falling in love with\na mortal only hastened his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just as you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:41.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tsukuyomaru swore he\nwould protect this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:44.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if he could not,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he threatened to abandon his\nduties as guardian of the barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and leave the tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:57.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even his heart had been\nstolen by a mortal woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You didn't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kill your own flesh\nand blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:16.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sent Tsukuyomaru\nto the netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:16.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:26.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as I had Shiori,\nhe was of no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Missus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:34.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Taigokumaru, you're unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:45.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori doesn't have the power\nto control the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:50.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if somehow, your sword breaks\nthrough the barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:54.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori will die with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you confident\nof success, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:04.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can he kill just Taigokumaru\nwithout hurting Shiori?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:08.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiori cannot control\nthe barrier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:11.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if Inuyasha can break through\nthe barrier...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}killing Taigokumaru\nwill also kill Shiori!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:20.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How will you kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup, old bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm no teasing up anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:27.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh? You eased up on me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:31.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then let me see...\nyour true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!\NBacklash Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:47.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, there's a crack in the barrier\nfrom the old bat's ghostly aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:51.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spiral of my Backlash Wave\nshould go through it and reach that bastard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ghostly aura from that brat's sword{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}is twisting into my ghostly aura\nand coming towards me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:01.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now go through and\nblast that bat's head off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? The barrier's bending!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:16.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? It's back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Taigokumaru isn't hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! I was a second too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:38.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good work, Shiori!\NThat's how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:40.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:45.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I avenge my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you, Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:06.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You, a half-demon,\ndare do this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:10.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never suspected she\nhad such power...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:17.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even I, Taigokumaru, could\nnot control the barrier!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- She's falling!\N- Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:28.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Even if my granddaughter\nis a half-demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I would never let\nmortals have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out! Shiori's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:36.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:41.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say your prayers, old bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:54.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Backlash Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:15.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I made you go through\nso much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:37.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing more to do here.\NLet's go, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:40.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Old Myoga, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:46.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten the purpose\nof your coming here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You needed to kill the demon who\nprotected the barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:52.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and allow Tetsusaiga to\nabsorb the blood
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:55.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to make it even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:58.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You came here to\nkill Shiori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... Well, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:05.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm not such\na jerk that I'd kill a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Especially, when she's such\na young innocent girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And she's also a half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll find someone else who puts up\nan even stronger barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and kill him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:18.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! You were never\nlike this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:18.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:24.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He means you've matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, we'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:31.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:36.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Break that sphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:57.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I want you to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:00.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This blood crystal is\nthe precious heirloom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:03.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,passed down to each guardian\nof the Demon Bat barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's from this crystal that\nwe obtain the power
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:08.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to put up a powerful barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:12.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And... it stores within itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the power of\neach generation of guardians,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,like my grandfather's and\nmy father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So if you break this crystal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:23.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think you'll be able to\nstrengthen your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We couldn't have asked\nfor anything better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, go ahead and break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:34.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The faster we break that sphere,\nthe better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:38.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sphere is releasing vapors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:45.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mommy, your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sphere put up a barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess it won't let me\nbreak it so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that makes it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...even more interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:09.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori, as if I'd let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:29.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Grandfather's voice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:35.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just releasing the sphere won't\nbreak your bond with the Demon Bats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:39.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even you, with a human mother...\na half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Taigokumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:46.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill you here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You old bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:49.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:54.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori! Come to hell\nwith the rest of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:02.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It got repelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:17.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you... Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The old bat's power is weakening!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now's my chance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let Shiori free!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sphere is shattering!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Finally, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:54.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My blade is turning red!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:01.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga absorbed the sphere's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which means the sword has\nincreased its power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:18.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:21.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one who\nsaved me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You weakened the old bat's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:30.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-uh. I didn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:35.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone's gentle arms embraced\nmy mommy and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and protected us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:43.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was Tsukuyomaru.\NYour father's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:53.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your father probably wished\nfor your freedom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:56.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Heh! Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:02.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha also wanted\nto rescue Shiori.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:14.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He probably forgot all about\nmaking Tetsusaiga stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:20.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why the spirit of Shiori's father\nlent Inuyasha a hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is Inuyasha thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:36.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How unusual for Inuyasha\nto contemplate about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:44.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But those two will probably\ngo through hard times still.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:48.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Don't worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:51.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't be a half-demon if\nyou're afraid of hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, we do have a fine example\nright here among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:59.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hopefully, Shiori doesn't turn\nout as warped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You guys're!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that's more like\nthe Inuyasha I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:12.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha deep in thought\njust {\i1}isn't{\i0} Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:16.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's right. Don't do something\nyou're not used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll drop ya both!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:20.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:23.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're just concerned about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:25.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, we are, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:27.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't take me for a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're all going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:33.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha didn't say a word\nwhen he left Shiori.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:38.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even a "Do your best"\nor "Hang in there."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:41.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though there were many things\nhe could say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:48.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha chose silence to\nencourage her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure she got his meaning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:55.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:56.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, don't treat me like a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:00.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:02.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Shippo! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:05.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...get on my nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Enough, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:08.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes! I never should a\ncome along!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:52.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon-cat siblings,\neach named for one of the four seasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:54.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Panther-Demon Tribe appears\nfrom the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:57.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Their aim-Sacred Jewel shards\nand Inuyasha's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:23:59.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.46,0:24:01.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It all started fifty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:04.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when Lord Sesshomaru meddled\nin the great war.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:07.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that around the time Inuyasha\nwas sealed to the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.37,0:24:11.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Plot of the Panther Devas"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:14.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is gonna be fun!\NI'll let 'em have it!
